
Project 1

 Chapter 1: Intro to HTML

 Metadata (in <head>): charset, viewport, description, author
 Sectioning/grouping/text-level: header, nav, main, section, article, footer, plus strong, em, span
 Link to CSS: <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
 Navigation list with links: <nav><ul><li><a href=...>
 Inline images: logo + dish photos (<img src="images/...">)
 Character references: &copy;, &amp;, &nbsp;

Chapter 2: Intro to CSS 

Format lists (menu categories, nav list)
 Background + text formatting (colors, fonts, line-height)
 Pseudo-classes/elements:
•	links: a:link, a:visited, a:hover, a:active
•	element: h2::after (add a decorative line)
   Contextual/attribute selectors (examples):
•	nav a { ... } (contextual)
•	a[href^="http"] { ... } (attribute selector)

Chapter 3: Page layouts 

 Block + floating elements
•	about.html: float chef/restaurant image left with text wrapping
 Floated layout
